Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with radio-resource management in a 3G LTE network. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses logistic regression for statistical learning. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with optimizing system parameters based on key performance indicators. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper proposes an automated healing method for troubleshooting. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also relevant as the paper uses an optimization engine to propose new parameter values.
